text: Grayson Bailey and Ethan Grant Dolan, generally known as The Dolan Twins (born December 16, 1999) are American twins who rose to fame through the former social media platform, Vine. Now with over 11 million subscribers on Youtube, the Twins have created an album and playlist, gone on an international tour called "4OU", won multiple Teen Choice Awards, and have been guests on the popular T.V. channel, MTV. They have also directed a LGBTQ+ music video for Australian band cubsport. Both twins have good looks, a great following, and an attitude that is mature and comedic for every range of age. Still they have so many more characteristics to define them.The set of twins are from the Long Valley section of Washington Township, Morris County, New Jersey.
